    {
      "para_id": "Q000990.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) In Karzida there never had been a ĝipar built and no en priestess had dwelt since the beginning of time , ( but now ) for Nanna of Karzida , his master , Amar-Suena , nominated by Enlil in Nibru , the steadfast supporter of Enlil's temple , the just god of his land , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , the beloved of Nanna , built his holy ĝipar in Karzida , ( and ) made En-agazid-ana , his beloved en priestess enter it . ( In so doing ) Amar-Suena will lengthen his life ."
    }
  ],
